contentrichtext.text: '''Lawrence County''' is the name of eleven counties in the United States. All but the one in South Dakota were named for the U.S. naval hero of the [[War of 1812]], Captain [[James Lawrence]]. * [[Lawrence County, Alabama]] * [[Lawrence County, Arkansas]] * [[Lawrence County, Illinois]] * [[Lawrence County, Indiana]] * [[Lawrence County, Kentucky]] * [[Lawrence County, Mississippi]] * [[Lawrence County, Missouri]] * [[Lawrence County, Ohio]] * [[Lawrence County, Pennsylvania]] * [[Lawrence County, South Dakota]] * [[Lawrence County, Tennessee]] {{Geodis|uscounty}}
